<sentence><enclosedCharacter>時</enclosedCharacter>イン１４時、アウト１１時。</sentence>
<sentence><enclosedCharacter>交</enclosedCharacter>雲仙バスターミナル→県営バス小浜温泉方面行きで５分、<image description="バス停" no="10" />西入口下車、徒歩２分。</sentence>
<sentence><enclosedCharacter>Ｐ</enclosedCharacter>３０台。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</listItem>
